Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.47,0:00:07.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.24,0:00:09.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was shocked when I found you collapsed on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.41,0:00:12.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I suddenly felt dizzy and tripped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.17,0:00:14.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for making you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.65,0:00:16.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you're slightly anemic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.13,0:00:16.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.99,0:00:18.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to go to the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.14,0:00:19.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.40,0:00:21.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I just need some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.74,0:00:24.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Remedial classes have started already.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.04,0:00:28.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't matter if you miss one day, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.20,0:00:29.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sleep today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.20,0:00:30.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.08,0:00:31.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san, what about your job?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.98,0:00:33.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take the day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.18,0:00:40.64,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\frz331.947\c&H82999C&\pos(726,166)}Day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.18,0:00:40.64,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\frz331.947\c&H82999C&\pos(558,74)}Month
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.18,0:00:40.64,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\frz331.947\c&H82999C&\pos(909,266)}Day of week
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.18,0:00:40.64,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\frz331.947\c&H82999C&\pos(1027,336)}Weather
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.18,0:00:40.64,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28\c&H8190A9&\frz25.38\pos(1142,467)}Clear
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.18,0:00:40.64,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28\c&H8190A9&\frz25.38\pos(828,275)}Thursday
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.18,0:00:40.64,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs48\frz329\pos(264,330)\c&H8190A9&}I went to school with Yukito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.18,0:00:40.64,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs48\pos(286,475)\frz329\c&H8190A9&}It was really fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.18,0:00:40.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I went to school with Yukito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.64,0:00:42.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I played with Yukito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.80,0:00:46.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A cicada flew into Yukito-san's breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.10,0:00:48.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I went to the train station with Yukito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.55,0:00:51.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I went to the shrine with Yukito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.20,0:00:54.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't read someone else's diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.79,0:00:57.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have anything else to write about?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.41,0:01:00.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That diary is my masterpiece.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.45,0:01:04.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, to put it bluntly, you don't have much talent for keeping a diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.41,0:01:07.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So from now on, write about what you want to do, not what you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.03,0:01:10.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not a diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.00,0:01:11.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's a diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.62,0:01:14.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make everything you write come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.02,0:01:20.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go to the beach with you, Yukito-san
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.81,0:01:24.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because we've never gone down to the beach together.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.08,0:01:28.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to dig in the sand and pick up pretty shells.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.14,0:01:29.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.82,0:01:32.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We see the beach all the time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.26,0:01:32.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gao!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.49,0:01:34.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.66,0:01:36.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.05,0:01:36.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.94,0:01:39.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go to the beach,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.09,0:01:40.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,together.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.34,0:01:42.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.87,0:03:27.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That child said she wanted to see the ocean,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.31,0:03:30.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but I couldn't take her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.73,0:03:39.23,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs54\c&HB83D41&\pos(643,96)}Episode 7
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.81,0:03:41.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu fainted?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.90,0:03:42.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.89,0:03:45.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She hasn't recovered yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:46.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's resting in her room now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.71,0:03:48.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.30,0:03:52.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll only feel worse if she sees my drunken face.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.70,0:03:54.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget that; I brought sushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.93,0:03:57.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's enjoy it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.50,0:04:01.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.62,0:04:03.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That really hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.20,0:04:06.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you take Misuzu in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.73,0:04:07.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.58,0:04:10.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you end up taking Misuzu in?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.40,0:04:13.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so she told you about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.18,0:04:18.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't take her in; she was pushed onto me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.49,0:04:20.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,even though I said I didn't want her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.85,0:04:23.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she isn't getting the love she needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.98,0:04:24.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:27.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only parent she has!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.44,0:04:31.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl has an episode whenever she becomes friends with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.65,0:04:34.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We never became close.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.49,0:04:37.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we can live together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.01,0:04:38.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is a parental relationship anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.92,0:04:41.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a real parent, so I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.17,0:04:45.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuck, wrong sushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.96,0:04:56.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The girl dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.30,0:04:58.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}First, it's a dream of the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.87,0:05:01.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The dreams keep going back in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.19,0:05:06.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They start to eat away at the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.23,0:05:09.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She starts to feel pain for no reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.34,0:05:12.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and, gradually, she begins to forget everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.22,0:05:18.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She begins to forget even her most precious friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.69,0:05:23.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And in the morning following her last dream, the girl will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.74,0:05:27.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She is always alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.59,0:05:31.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If she becomes close to someone, both will become sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.65,0:05:33.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Neither will survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.02,0:05:36.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So the girl told me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:38.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Stay away from me."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:42.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She was a very kind and strong girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.21,0:05:43.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's why I was able to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.01,0:05:46.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But she...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:52.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the sky, there is a girl with wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.47,0:05:54.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She is always alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.51,0:05:56.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She vanishes before becoming an adult,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.67,0:05:59.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}repeating such sad dreams endlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.08,0:06:05.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going on a trip?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.60,0:06:08.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I'll travel around by myself, visiting hot springs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:11.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.31,0:06:13.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Misuzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.71,0:06:15.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving her in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.15,0:06:19.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't get too close to her, those attacks won't happen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:20.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.00,0:06:23.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu is dreaming now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.25,0:06:26.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The dreams are making her behave like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.13,0:06:26.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.91,0:06:29.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I remembered a story my mother told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.29,0:06:33.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother had met a girl with the same kind of sickness a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.98,0:06:37.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After a while, Misuzu will begin to forget: about me and about you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:43.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, after having her last dream, she'll probably die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.01,0:06:44.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.54,0:06:48.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, there are jokes you can make and those you shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.54,0:06:49.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.99,0:06:50.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.85,0:06:52.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.04,0:06:53.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.94,0:06:58.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.70,0:07:01.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.59,0:07:02.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.41,0:07:04.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:06.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard Mommy's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.87,0:07:10.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she's going away for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.08,0:07:11.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.72,0:07:16.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I love Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.69,0:07:23.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:32.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Take your time. Don't push yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.54,0:07:33.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.79,0:07:36.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a crow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.90,0:07:40.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:41.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.50,0:07:44.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.20,0:07:45.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.88,0:07:47.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.48,0:07:50.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,V!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.26,0:07:53.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I've walked this road many times before,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.73,0:07:56.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,was the ocean always this far?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.47,0:08:02.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.29,0:08:07.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:12.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I... again...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.89,0:08:14.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet another attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.61,0:08:15.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.29,0:08:20.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get better soon... so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.26,0:08:23.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the ocean... tomorrow, instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.71,0:08:31.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you better now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.19,0:08:33.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.89,0:08:35.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:36.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.63,0:08:38.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I had another dream last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.96,0:08:41.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This time it was a happy one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:44.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it was nighttime, the sky was really bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.34,0:08:47.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it was a festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.10,0:08:49.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was watching it from afar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.54,0:08:51.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.14,0:08:52.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yukito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.46,0:08:53.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:58.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The person you're looking for and my dreams are connected, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:08:59.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.77,0:09:01.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They could be unrelated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:07.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've thought about this a lot, and I think I know the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.07,0:09:08.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you listen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.64,0:09:12.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My dreams represent my other self.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.24,0:09:15.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And that girl is suffering right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.89,0:09:18.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try my best to dream
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.92,0:09:22.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because they might help me understand her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.94,0:09:27.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I do that, I might be able to help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.26,0:09:33.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san, it's not a coincidence that I started having these dreams, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.35,0:09:36.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt that this summer was special.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.86,0:09:39.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to try my best to make a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.51,0:09:43.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I met you and started having those dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.11,0:09:45.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're probably all connected, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.30,0:09:48.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I want to do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.69,0:09:51.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make this summer the happiest ever
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:53.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because it's the summer that I met you, Yukito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:09:58.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.59,0:10:02.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.05,0:10:04.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.66,0:10:09.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.72,0:10:10.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.58,0:10:12.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.87,0:10:14.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.93,0:10:16.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My feet won't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.04,0:10:30.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should call Hijiri
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:32.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,or even a large hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.11,0:10:34.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.55,0:10:37.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think a doctor can cure me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.33,0:10:40.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san, you know it too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.63,0:10:44.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My dreams are making me this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.52,0:10:45.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.73,0:10:48.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I had another dream last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.17,0:10:49.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was about a journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.66,0:10:50.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A journey?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.66,0:10:52.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.63,0:10:56.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I walked through the forest for days and days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.23,0:10:58.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was hard, but I kept going
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.68,0:11:01.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because I had someone special with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.45,0:11:02.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone special?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:08.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that every time I have a dream, I get a little weaker,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:11.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,until finally, I, like the girl in the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.69,0:11:11.54,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.54,0:11:12.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.68,0:11:15.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I got scolded.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.35,0:11:18.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to think about your other self.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.48,0:11:20.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just worry about getting better for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.59,0:11:21.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.38,0:11:22.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu-chin is a strong girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:50.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.45,0:11:52.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san! Yukito-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.72,0:11:55.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.34,0:11:56.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.06,0:12:00.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be nothing with a face like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.59,0:12:02.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My face has always been like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:04.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu, go back to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.33,0:12:06.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't leave you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.35,0:12:07.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.77,0:12:09.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me worry about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:10.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.46,0:12:22.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this scar?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.96,0:12:29.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.39,0:12:31.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu, hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:36.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.64,0:12:44.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.39,0:12:47.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be better soon, so stay here with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.47,0:12:49.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I'm close to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.25,0:12:52.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. Stay here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.78,0:12:59.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does everyone leave me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.69,0:13:06.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.59,0:13:07.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.92,0:13:09.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you, Yukito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.22,0:13:10.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing wrong with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.98,0:13:11.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.94,0:13:13.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I call Hijiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.44,0:13:14.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Or Kano?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.60,0:13:16.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Minagi... is out of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.90,0:13:18.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So maybe someone from your class?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.00,0:13:19.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.35,0:13:21.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to bother them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.26,0:13:22.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.80,0:13:24.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You want friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.10,0:13:25.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to be alone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:27.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.74,0:13:30.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you're here, I don't need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:32.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that trouble you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.52,0:13:33.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:38.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go to the beach with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.77,0:13:40.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to play on the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.49,0:13:43.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to race and splash water at each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.64,0:13:46.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and when we're finished, we'll say, "See you tomorrow!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.04,0:13:48.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But for now, I'll wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.95,0:13:52.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll be even happier when I finally do go to the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.98,0:13:54.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizusu-chin, fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.13,0:13:58.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.05,0:13:58.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.86,0:14:00.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I plan on leaving soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.77,0:14:01.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.15,0:14:08.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I stay with you any longer, neither of us will live,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.79,0:14:12.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so I've decided to run away from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:16.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave this town and go somewhere where I won't ever see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.07,0:14:17.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.27,0:14:18.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.40,0:14:22.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We've become... too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.24,0:14:27.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.53,0:14:29.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.85,0:14:34.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I should've played by myself like this all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.25,0:14:35.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.91,0:14:38.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.44,0:14:39.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This summer break,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:42.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,this summer break that I spent with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.21,0:14:45.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.50,0:14:46.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.55,0:14:47.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.88,0:14:51.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any more buses?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.89,0:14:53.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:14:57.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.65,0:15:02.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, in my dream this morning, I was locked up in a room all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:03.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.37,0:15:08.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was waiting a long time for someone to come and let me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.04,0:15:12.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I want to go with you, Yukito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.62,0:15:15.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there no way for me to go with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.04,0:15:18.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I want to leave this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:19.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just have to stay away from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.96,0:15:24.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I leave you, you should recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.81,0:15:28.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I can't be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:29.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.39,0:15:30.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.80,0:15:34.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for saying stupid things again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.07,0:15:34.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:38.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.21,0:15:39.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.13,0:15:40.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.40,0:15:41.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.05,0:15:42.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.30,0:15:44.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you're alone, stay strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.25,0:15:44.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.90,0:15:46.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hang in there even if I'm alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:48.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a strong girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.20,0:15:49.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:50.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.92,0:15:53.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.31,0:15:58.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.29,0:16:26.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking now, Yukito?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.34,0:16:28.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want your audience to laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.25,0:16:31.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't, the doll won't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.75,0:16:32.92,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\pos(638,219)\c&HAEDCDD&}Ocean Taxi Ferry Peer
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.34,0:16:33.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wishing for it to move isn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.65,0:16:35.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to reach further.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.45,0:16:36.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Only then will it move.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.99,0:16:42.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.09,0:16:44.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.42,0:16:51.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That child said she wanted to see the ocean,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.05,0:16:54.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but I couldn't take her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.30,0:16:55.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.53,0:16:58.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,this time, I want you to save her for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.59,0:17:03.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside this doll, there are wishes that were never granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.79,0:17:07.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother, and my mother's mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.46,0:17:12.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,before losing their strength, sealed their power inside this doll
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.06,0:17:15.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,for the day when someone is ready to release their wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:20.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I will become one of those wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.52,0:17:23.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How you will use it is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.62,0:17:26.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can forget about the girl in the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.39,0:17:30.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but Yukito...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.42,0:17:34.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In a town somewhere, you are sure to meet a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.76,0:17:38.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you really wish to save her, no matter what,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.03,0:17:41.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,then put your heart and soul into the doll
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.04,0:17:44.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because I will be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.90,0:17:49.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Put my heart and soul... into the doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.64,0:17:54.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's been wrong with this guy for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.63,0:17:59.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's sick from this heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.01,0:18:04.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.31,0:18:08.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.43,0:18:09.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.98,0:18:14.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to watch this and tell me how I can make it fun so that people laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.06,0:18:16.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.80,0:18:17.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.86,0:18:20.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not that fun, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.35,0:18:21.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.80,0:18:25.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you try doing more instead of just making it walk around?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.98,0:18:28.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Make it like a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.00,0:18:32.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Make it dance or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:33.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.44,0:18:37.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It has to be more original.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.84,0:18:43.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.73,0:18:57.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.56,0:18:58.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That show was fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.46,0:18:59.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was fun and cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.70,0:19:00.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.56,0:19:03.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks a lot for staying this long.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.20,0:19:05.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well mister, good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.71,0:19:07.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.67,0:19:25.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu, I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.07,0:19:28.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.83,0:19:31.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay with you and continue to make you laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.18,0:19:33.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.74,0:19:35.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I learned some tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.32,0:19:37.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're definitely funny,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.14,0:19:39.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so watch carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.86,0:19:44.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.04,0:19:48.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.31,0:19:49.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.34,0:19:50.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.43,0:19:59.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why didn't I realize it sooner?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.99,0:20:03.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was happy just being here with you and watching you smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.89,0:20:08.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I just did that, I was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.91,0:20:11.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't go anywhere anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.14,0:20:13.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stay with me and keep smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.15,0:20:15.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okay, Misuzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.02,0:20:23.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.35,0:20:27.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You must remember what you need to do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.49,0:20:32.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I... I want to be with Misuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.05,0:20:35.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I could, I'd go back to when we first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.63,0:20:37.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.58,0:20:39.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}with Misuzu... forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.12,0:20:44.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.80,0:20:49.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.59,0:20:52.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I couldn't get up anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.10,0:20:54.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.62,0:20:56.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.44,0:20:58.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You came back, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.03,0:21:02.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm better again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.67,0:21:04.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I can try my hardest again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.85,0:21:06.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yukito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.15,0:21:17.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Argh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.42,0:21:23.42,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,449)\fs54\fad(1100,0)}Shōryaku Era: Year 5
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.42,0:21:25.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.66,0:21:29.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You... what are you doing in such a place?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.47,0:21:32.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have time to talk, hurry up and get off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.35,0:21:35.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're... not someone I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.27,0:21:38.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Senior Assistant Lieutenant of the Outer Palace Guard, Ryuuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.93,0:21:42.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And you... where do you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.07,0:21:44.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.20,0:21:45.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.16,0:21:46.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We just met.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.25,0:21:48.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.84,0:21:51.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'm not that well-known.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.85,0:21:53.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.10,0:21:54.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.80,0:21:57.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The winged person I was ordered to protect is also called Kanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.62,0:21:59.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that truly is a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.87,0:22:01.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it is really.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.88,0:22:07.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.97,0:23:42.77,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\fad(500,900)\fs51\shad2.25\pos(641,293)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.57,0:23:46.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A winged person is a messenger of the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.84,0:23:50.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In times of famine or disease, they are able to speak directly with the gods
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.98,0:23:54.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,through their spiritual powers and prayers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.75,0:23:59.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Being a family means you can lean on one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.41,0:24:03.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.33,0:24:07.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought that being alone would be this painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.92,0:24:20.17,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(950,0)\fs39\fscx100\fscy100\shad2.4\c&HFEFEFA&\4c&H121213&\pos(916,419)}Episode 8
